Current interation
====================

Objective: 
  To allow that someone plug in the Payment model in a new project.

Tasks:
  x Create Payment model with basic fields: description, due date, payment
    date, due value, payment value.
  x Create commons scopes: revenue, cost, open, confirmed and with_interest.
  - Add polymorphic association to allow associate payments to a any model,
    like a client or a contract.
  x Test Payment model
  - Publish the gem

Backlog:
